DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([Id] bigint, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [AbpPermissions] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, 0),
(@p7, @p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, 1),
(@p14, @p15, @p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, 2),
(@p21, @p22, @p23, @p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, 3)) AS i ([CreationTime], [CreatorUserId], [Discriminator], [IsGranted], [Name], [RoleId], [TenantId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([CreationTime], [CreatorUserId], [Discriminator], [IsGranted], [Name], [RoleId], [TenantId])
VALUES (i.[CreationTime], i.[CreatorUserId], i.[Discriminator], i.[IsGranted], i.[Name], i.[RoleId], i.[TenantId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [AbpPermissions] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
